    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233040/extras/d4dd0a808e0187aee7bda053b98de4b0.avif?t=1714725989\" width=467 height=70 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Remember Super Mario Bros?</h2><br>Okay so this is game is pretty like the same, but with a twist.<br>Hope you'll find a way out of this place...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Choose your character between 2 colors</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play through 9 levels over 2 maps</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Avoid as many obstacles as possible</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play with a friend on the same screen</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Create your own levels with the built in level editor</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose your style</h2><br>Select the player you want to play with.<br><br><strong>Red</strong>                      <strong>Blue</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233040/extras/99db197a66da298acb3b8ac5cbb5c17b.webp?t=1714725989\" width=58 height=58 /></span>                  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233040/extras/f093607d5a21432ccd4d9b430f4c02e2.webp?t=1714725989\" width=58 height=58 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Go through 2 maps</h2><br>Travel over 2 maps composed in a total of 9 levels with more<br>obstacles than you could except.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233040/extras/caab6bd8fb5c4b3dd404f1d29d72c507.avif?t=1714725989\" width=256 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Invite a friend to join you</h2><br>Play with a friend on the same screen at home or with<br>the Steam Remote Play Together.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233040/extras/48eae7a2928b421b0900c13ccd32745b.avif?t=1714725989\" width=110 height=154 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Let's see some of the things you could encounter during your journey</h2><br><strong>Spikes</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233040/extras/a8b435b8a8b239a007005fa9dc6129b4.webp?t=1714725989\" width=111 height=47 /></span><br><br><strong>Rock</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233040/extras/0915213cde288e3fb164efc82ffbbc66.webp?t=1714725989\" width=190 height=55 /></span><br><br><strong>Knife</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233040/extras/d7fb237eb863d9df51ad7fb5b40a445b.avif?t=1714725989\" width=162 height=64 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Express yourself with the map editor</h2><br>Create your own level of SuperJumpWorld Rage and play or<br>share it with your friend to see their anger.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233040/extras/da79747677b84a572fc3f7a7c82a6e67.avif?t=1714725989\" width=266 height=184 /></span>",
